txt.en: Mizâdi requests your presence in investigating a strange report she has received from her scouts.
Speak with Mizâdi in Urmâkh. Urmâkh can be found in Imhûlar, which is within the Ikorbân Valley.
Mizâdi, Shâra of Renewed Hamât, requests your presence in Urmâkh. She calls for your aid in investigating a disturbing report she has received from her scouts to the south.
'Thank you for your haste in seeking me out. I received a disturbing report from one of my scouts that I would discuss with you.'
Speak with Mizâdi in Urmâkh. Urmâkh can be found in Imhûlar, which is within the Ikorbân Valley.
